    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>ground coriander</strong> to the pot and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
