      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped potatoes </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>to the pot with 550ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[825ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.1L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 15-18 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender – this is your <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>soup base</strong></p>",
