    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> mayo</strong> with a pinch of<strong> pepper</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic aioli</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p>",
