    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are fork tender, add the <strong>roasted pepper & tomato </strong>to the <strong>smoky soup base</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong> – this is your <strong>plant-based smoky pepper & tomato soup</strong></p><p>Place the <strong>halved ciabatta[s]</strong> in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p>",
